# the silver searcher
on linux: https://github.com/ggreer/the_silver_searcher
on windows/cygwin: https://github.com/ggreer/the_silver_searcher/wiki/Windows
on cywgin:
if you don't have apt-cyg
wget rawgit.com/transcode-open/apt-cyg/master/apt-cyg
install apt-cyg /bin
then
apt-cyg install automake pkg-config gcc-core libpcre-devel liblzma-devel make
git clone git://github.com/ggreer/the_silver_searcher.git
cd the_silver_searcher
./build.sh && make install


